# reopen-malformed.persona — input robustness ON THE REOPENED decision (REQ-C1.5,
# REQ-C1.2). The level is changed (reopening the dependent decision), then the
# reopened decision gets a garbage answer first (which must re-prompt, symmetric
# with the initial ask) and a valid answer next. Turn map: 1 level(novice),
# 2 decision(alpha), 3 level-restate(expert -> changed), 4 garbage(reopen re-ask),
# 5 valid option-beta(reopen re-ask), 6 sign-off.
expertise=novice
answer.1=novice
answer.2=option-alpha
answer.3=expert
answer.4=@@garbage-reopen@@
answer.5=option-beta
answer.6=record-approval
